 r‚Üêpars AttachWCExpect spec;‚éïIO;par0;par;bpos;bsize;attach;h0;w0;h;w;t;l;bh;bw;ec;topN;botN;leftN;rightN;posn;size
‚çù Attach-correct geometry for one box. Left: (par0 par) = parent baseline and
‚çù current size. Right: spec = (posn size attach). Returns (posn size).
‚çù Each edge: attached to the NEAR parent edge ‚Üí fixed (c0); to the FAR edge ‚Üí
‚çù fixed distance from it (shifts by the size change); 'None' ‚Üí proportional.
‚çù Whole px; Size never negative. Same math as the client's attachGeometry.
